{"tid":2745,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派：不認同鄭松泰倒轉國旗行為","createTime":"2016-11-26T01:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T02:06:26.000Z","uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92312dec7909665acaa247278500a94a917999ae","tid":2745,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會內委會討論謝偉俊計劃動議譴責熱血公民鄭松泰，多名民主派議員表明不認同鄭松泰把國旗和區旗倒轉，但批評謝偉俊的動議是將政治鬥爭帶入議會。謝偉俊重申事件非常嚴重，必須嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊計劃動議譴責鄭松泰，多名民主派議員在內委會上表明，不認同鄭松泰把國旗和區旗倒轉的行為，但批評有關動議是將政治鬥爭帶入議會。<br />\n<br />\n事件主角鄭松泰認為主席梁君彥當日已就他的行為作出裁決，建制派議員亦已報警。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊重申事態嚴重，必須嚴肅處理，<br />\n<br />\n根據議事規則，動議會提交上大會處理，再交付調查委員會調查，等委員會完成調查工作後，向立法會提交報告，再讓議員就報告辯論和表決，如獲出席會議的三分二議員通過譴責，立法會主席便可宣告鄭松泰喪失議員資格。"},{"pid":"0de93161d7e175239d7b145332cc427c9187d3f7","tid":2745,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:51:27.000Z","msg":"割完一個又一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91386e4891ed4f1f73b5034e516717ecdd89cf1a","tid":2745,"uid":2864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ae019858e153b79eab5eeb5121afd06c1d874d","tid":2745,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"泛民想搞到自己愈黎愈少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea2c62d304668fc70f9912d36e18b56d458ef44","tid":2745,"uid":12712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"家陣立會真係好低汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}